data.description: Amazing wonderful home with 3 bedroom/ 2 bath home in South Lehigh Acres/This fabulous property is ideal for any type of buyer/ the split floor plan allows for privacy in your room/ away from the other bedrooms! Volume ceilings/ raised panel doors through out/ Master has large walk-in closet/ walk-in shower and soaking tub in Master Bathroom add to the many amenities/ Spacious Family Room with Dining room adjacent, Kitchen has Stainless Steel Appliances (Refrigerator, Flat Top Stove/Oven, Microwave, & Dishwasher). Sliding doors leading to the Fully Screened Under Truss Lanai from both the Eating area and Family Room/ Indoor Laundry Room/ The back of the home has a simple concrete slab open air patio with room for a pool/ You have to see this beautiful home close to Bell Blvd and SR-82/ A great looking and immaculate home ready to move in/ Located just minutes from Fort Myers on a quiet road/ Schedule your showing appointment Now!
